{"title":"汉俳五首","authors":["钟敬文"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉俳五首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟敬文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本爱媛大学副教授加藤千代女士乘暑假之暇，重访北京，并将应邀赴太原，考察山西民间文艺。欢叙之余，作汉俳五首以张其行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重踏神京土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像女儿回到娘家，①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦样的喜悦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛往年时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对坐晴窗谈学艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深言忘酷暑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱车太原去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那晋祠里的残柏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘唤起幽情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽汾河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我淌过汗的土地，②"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将微笑迎你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民艺海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一度轻帆远驶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得意浪花中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"①  加藤女士几年前曾在北师大进修。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②  一九七一年，我曾在临汾北师大分校劳动锻炼。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}